See Social Media Engagement - Fast!

Our Social Media Monitoring Tool offers a simple, streamlined and free way to collect data points on social media engagement with your chosen URL. It’s as easy as 1,2,3.

  1. Input your URL and the Social Media Monitoring Tool will collect the data online.
  2. Get the stats - social media engagement broken down numerically from platform to platform, as well as graph interpretations of the data and our own MarketingTool.io Score.
  3. Download PDF lets you grab the results and share them with whoever you need.

The Time Saving Audit Tool For Social Media Marketers

Social Media Monitoring Tool takes the hassle out of your next social media marketing audit. If you’re offering social media services, click Download PDF to get a quick, up-to-date social engagement overview for your clients. Measure how your campaign is tracking by checking in each month, and see which platforms work best for your brand to refine your strategy!
